                            <comment id="12837179" author="bgillis" created="Tue, 23 Feb 2010 10:06:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A sample pdf file to reproduce the bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12837180" author="bgillis" created="Tue, 23 Feb 2010 10:11:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The sample pdf file printed to Microsoft XPS Document Writer&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12837187" author="bgillis" created="Tue, 23 Feb 2010 10:28:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue exists also in pdfbox 0.8.0-incubating.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12848772" author="msahyoun" created="Tue, 23 Mar 2010 15:58:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the issues also occurs using the latest trunk but on Windows only (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-632&quot; title=&quot;Invalid page rendering while printing a PDF with an image inside.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-632&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-632&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.out.win.pdf). Mac and Linux work fine (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-632&quot; title=&quot;Invalid page rendering while printing a PDF with an image inside.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-632&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-632&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.out.pdf). Printing the pages individually on Windows produces the expected results. What&apos;s also visible from the result on Windows is that the box on the first pages seems to be used as a clipping path for the text on the second page.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12848844" author="lehmi" created="Tue, 23 Mar 2010 18:44:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve applied a patch with version 926714.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch ensures that the clipping path is never null. I&apos;d already made a similar patch with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-552&quot; title=&quot;NPE while printing a pdf with an image inside&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-552&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-552&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but obviously it wasn&apos;t good enough.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks to Maruan for the testing and his conclusion. It was the hint which led me to the solution.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
